            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine your<strong> lamb mince</strong> and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) in a large bowl with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until thoroughly combined (clean hands is the best way!)</p><p>Divide them and shape into 5 meatballs per person – these are your <strong>lamb meatballs</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
