        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>lettuce leaves</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Combine your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped garlic</strong> in a small bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>garlic yoghurt</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1680105161036-x200.jpg",
