            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>baharat </strong>and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, remove the pot from the heat, then add the <strong>drained couscous</strong>, <strong>cumin roasted carrot & onion</strong> and <strong>beef stock mix </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>baharat spiced giant couscous</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
