        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>torn lettuce leaves</strong> in wide bowl topped with the <strong>baharat spiced giant couscous</strong> and <strong>browned lamb meatballs</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>garlic yoghurt</strong> and top with the <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
